title: FUBAR Registry Destroyer 2014
description:
FUBAR Registry Destroyer 2014
-----------------------------

A new version in this evil series of applications!

This version will wipe clean Windows Registry, meaning that nothing works anymore.

NO USER-DATA WILL BE DELETED!!!

Windows might show these data as non-existing, but that is because the Registry has been deleted, and Windows is not able to find anything at all.


There is no installation.

Setup is as usual:
You get 2 warnings, telling you what you are about to do.

This application will run immediately thereafter. It will never run again; nothing is installed!
